HOTEL-REVEIWES:
This is a web page that allows its users to comment on various meals in various hotels.

![PHASE-PROJECT-101](./images/project.png)

Users can::
1.Post a comment
2.post an image
3.Post a rating
4.Post the restaurant they are in.
5.You can also edit or delete a comment.


Technologies Used:
HTML
CSS
JS
db.json


